314
00:33:59,898 --> 00:34:01,275
Baik.

315
00:34:20,919 --> 00:34:22,421
Kenapa kau mengikat dirimu?

316
00:34:22,963 --> 00:34:25,924
Siapa tahu aku
tidur berjalan lagi.

317
00:35:51,802 --> 00:35:53,262
Ibu?

318
00:35:57,808 --> 00:35:59,101
Johnny?

319
00:38:52,942 --> 00:38:57,572
- Janet! Ada apa? Kenapa?
- Ada seseorang di kamar!

320
00:38:58,615 --> 00:39:00,909
Tidak ada siapa-siapa!
Apa maksudmu?

321
00:39:02,952 --> 00:39:04,496
Ada seseorang!

322
00:39:10,293 --> 00:39:12,087
- Ada seseorang di kamar kami!
- Apa?

323
00:39:12,170 --> 00:39:14,172
- Ranjang kami berguncang.
- Janet!

324
00:39:14,255 --> 00:39:17,050
- Jika kau mengada-ada...
