00:48:02,285 --> 00:48:04,454
Siapa kau?

385
00:48:08,375 --> 00:48:09,960
Katakan siapa dirimu!

386
00:48:10,043 --> 00:48:11,920
Ibu! Bangun!

387
00:48:12,003 --> 00:48:13,672
Apa maumu?

388
00:48:20,011 --> 00:48:21,680
Maafkan aku, Lorraine.

389
00:48:30,564 --> 00:48:32,190
